    title: "Tackling San Antonio's Hard Water: An Honest Look at Clean Water Services San Antonio",
    excerpt: "San Antonio residents know the drill: chalky residue on showerheads, spots on dishes, and that slightly dry feeling after a shower. The culprit? Our city's water, primarily sourced from the Edwards Aquifer. While clean and safe to drink, it's notorious for its high mineral content and significant...",
