    excerpt: "For anyone who\u2019s lived in Las Vegas for more than a few weeks, the chalky residue on showerheads, the perpetually streaky dishes, and the dry, itchy skin are all too familiar. This isn't just an inconvenience; it's a daily reminder of the exceptionally hard water flowing through the taps of the L...",
