    excerpt: "Austin, Texas, is known for its vibrant culture, live music, and beautiful natural springs. But when it comes to the water flowing from your tap, the story can be a little more complex. Sourced primarily from the Colorado River and Lake Travis, Austin's water is moderately hard and experiences se...",
