    title: "Solving NYC's Lead Problem: A Look at Tankless Filter's Innovative Approach",
    excerpt: "New York City's tap water is famously sourced from pristine upstate reservoirs, earning it a reputation for quality. It's naturally soft and tastes good, but beneath the surface of this impressive system lies a challenge many residents face daily: **aging building infrastructure**. While the wate...",
