    excerpt: "Phoenix, a vibrant desert metropolis, boasts a unique water story. Sourcing primarily from the majestic Salt and Verde Rivers, supplemented by the Colorado River, the city's water supply is robust. However, the arid climate and extensive distribution networks contribute to a common challenge for ...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
