    id: 475,
    slug: "water-plant-miami",
    title: "Unpacking Miami's Tap Water: The Critical Role of Water Plant",
    excerpt: "Miami residents often wonder about the quality of the water flowing from their taps. Given South Florida's unique geography and climate, the region's water supply presents distinct challenges. At the heart of ensuring safe, clean drinking water for the community is **Water Plant**, a key municipa...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
