    excerpt: "Orlando, the heart of Central Florida, is renowned for its theme parks, sunny weather, and vibrant community. But beneath the surface, many residents know another truth: the local water can present its own set of challenges. Drawn primarily from groundwater sources, Orlando's tap water often grap...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
