    excerpt: "Denver, a city celebrated for its stunning mountain backdrop and outdoor lifestyle, often takes pride in its pristine, snowmelt-fed water supply. On the surface, our water seems ideal \u2013 naturally soft and sourced from high-altitude watersheds. However, a deeper dive reveals that the journey from ...",
