    title: "Beyond the Tap: Understanding Atlanta's Water and Home Treatment Options with Water Softener Installation",
    excerpt: "For residents of Atlanta, ensuring the quality of the water flowing into their homes is a common concern. While our drinking water typically meets federal standards, many homeowners seek to go a step further, addressing specific characteristics of local water and enhancing their daily experience....",
    date: "2026-03-17",
