    title: "Taming Austin's Tap: How Water Softener Installation by Kinsey Plumbing Services Addresses Local Water Challenges",
    excerpt: "Austin, a city celebrated for its vibrant culture and natural beauty, draws its municipal water primarily from the Colorado River and Lake Travis. While generally safe to drink, residents often experience a common nuisance: moderately hard water. This isn't just an aesthetic issue; it can lead to...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
