    excerpt: "New York, a city famed for its vibrant life and iconic skyline, often boasts about the quality of its tap water, sourced from pristine upstate reservoirs. For many residents, a glass of water straight from the tap is a given. However, beneath this general assurance lies a more nuanced reality, pa...",
