    excerpt: "Chicago boasts one of the most iconic skylines in the world, and its lifeblood \u2013 Lake Michigan \u2013 provides drinking water for millions. While generally considered a high-quality source, the reality for many residents, particularly those in older neighborhoods, presents a more complex picture. Here...",
