    excerpt: "Miami, a vibrant city known for its stunning coastline and energetic atmosphere, relies on the Biscayne Aquifer for its water supply. While this natural resource is vital, it presents unique challenges for homeowners and businesses alike. From the tell-tale taste of chlorine to the stubborn resid...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
