    excerpt: "Denver, the Mile High City, boasts a stunning natural landscape, fed by pristine Rocky Mountain snowmelt. This source provides Denver residents with water that is, by nature, refreshingly soft. However, as any local knows, the journey from mountain peak to household tap isn't always smooth. An ag...",
    date: "2026-03-17",
