    title: "Navigating Dallas Water: A Look at Whole House Water Filter's Solutions",
    excerpt: "For Dallas residents, the quality of tap water is a frequent topic of conversation. Sourced from area reservoirs, Dallas's water typically presents as moderately hard, ranging from **8-12 grains per gallon (GPG)**. This level of hardness, coupled with **seasonal fluctuations in chlorine and turbi...",
